### Android Exception Details

Shows all details about a single exception. This dashboard is meant to be opened from the "Android Application Overview" dashboard by selecting a specific crash from the crashes list to see its details.

_stacktrace.group_id.customDescription: Internal field used by Elastic dashboards. Do not use in user queries.

embeddableConfig.description: Shows the top sessions with the most occurrences of this exception. A session is a period of time during which a user interacts with the application to accomplish a single task or goal. Ideally, a session should represent an isolated user interaction with the application.
embeddableConfig.title: Top affected sessions
